column2: SELECT   p.ra,   p.dec,   z.z,   z.zErr,      q =    CASE     WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVAB_r     WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expAB_r   END,   phi =    CASE     WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVPhi_r     WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expPhi_r   END,    p.petroMag_r,   p.petroMag_u,   p.fracDeV_r into mydb.one_sample_target from PhotoObj p      JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n ON n.objID = p.objID   JOIN Photoz z ON z.objID = n.objID  WHERE   p.type = #   AND z.z < # + #*z.zErr   AND z.z > # - #*z.zErr
